snippet.title: Wiara
snippet.description:
Hey there, my name is Tanui aka Wiara. I am the founder of this channel and also the 'Lofi Wiara' music channel.

FunFact ~ Wiara is a Polish word which translates to 'Faith' or 'Belief' in English
